Hosting provider of slash16.org is aws.amazon.com.

To find the provider of the given website there is a lot of solution :
1.	`whois` utility that can provide a lot of information.
	REGISTRY - is the company which manages the list of a set of domain names.
	REGISTRANT - is the legal owner of the domain who registered it.
	REGISTRAR - a company that help to look up and register a domain name.
	whois slash16.org | awk '/(Registrar|registrar):/ { print; exit }'
	whois slash16.org | awk '/Name Server:/ { print; exit }'

2.	Use a dedicate service to look up details like : whoishostingthis.com or
	hostingcompass.com
